Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US import restrictions, March 1975
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8qk1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Mar 1975
US import restrictions. Possible trade with Cuba. No support for Cambodia. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less